==English==
{{wikipedia}}
===Etymology===
From {{bor|en|grc|Ξενοφῶν}}.
===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}
# [[Athenian]] [[historian]] and [[philosopher]] born 427 {{B.C.E.}} and author of the ''Anabasis'' and ''Memorabilia''. He was a [[pupil]] of [[Socrates]] and became a [[general]] during the [[Persian]] wars.
